headline: Trump efforts to roll back solar credits add urgency for Rancho Viejo backers
summary: The Trump administration’s rollback of tax credits for renewable energy projects adds a sense of urgency to a controversial solar project south of Santa Fe. AES Corp. now must break ground on the Rancho Viejo Solar project by year’s end to secure federal tax credits.
